## Why add Load Balancer?

Distributes requests across multiple servers.

Improves availability.

Distribution Algorithm

Round Robin

Request 1 → Server 1

Request 2 → Server 2

Request 3 → Server 1

...

Active-Active

Both servers receive traffic.

Active-Passive

One server works.

Second waits until failure.

Primary-Replica Database

Primary accepts writes.

Replica copies data.

Applications usually read from Replica and write to Primary.

Issues

No firewall.

No HTTPS.

No monitoring.

Still SPOF if HAProxy fails.
